# Crossvader.com - Playlist

Playlist is a service that exposes a REST API allowing consumers to view 
playlists for a given artist name and concert date.

## Playlists Collection [/v1/playlists{?artist_name,concert_date}]

### List All Playlists [GET]

You may restrict/filter playlists by `artist_name` and `concert_date`. Each 
Playlist returns a `concert` along with `tracks` in JSON format.

+ Parameters

    + artist_name (optional) - Artist name
    + concert_date (optional) - Concert date

+ Response 200 (application/json)

